#: ../../R/raster-blaster.rst:9
msgid ""
"[Cambridge] Specialized hardware for :ref:`bitblt` operations (a "
":ref:`blitter`\\). Allegedly inspired by ‘Rasta Blasta’, British slang for "
"the sort of portable stereo Americans call a ‘boom box’ or ‘ghetto blaster’."
msgstr ""
"[Cambridge] \\ :ref:`bitblt`\\ 操作のための専用ハードウェア(\\ "
":ref:`blitter`\\)。アメリカ人が‘boom box’や‘ghetto "
"blaster’と呼ぶ種類のポータブルステレオを指すイギリスの俗語‘Rasta Blasta’に着想を得たとされる。"
